    "1027411191221994792007/06/27 15:08:36MarrnIt's not necessary to wear tanking gear as a feral druid.  Just wear your dps gear and switch to bear form after you convert your first 5 combo points.",
    "10274201815102018152007/12/15 14:49:27geordiesiYep, soloable by 70 Prot Warrior too with pretty avarage geens/blues, in battle stance, no potion needed. \
