    "1027420629511720052007/12/24 00:06:29vexis58Same as a ret pally. I used Hammer of Justice once during the fight so I could cast two heals on myself while he was stunned, but he was down before I even had to bubble/bandage.",
    "10274126654101266542007/07/25 14:22:33PavarialSolo'd as a decently geared combat rogue, took me two tries, but the ethereals nearby were kind enough to supply me with blinding and flash powder.",
