    "10274123305101233052007/07/19 10:44:44GogeyVery easy solo, even as a survival hunter.\
\
Strat:\
\
1: Clear around the bones, he WILL pull most of what you dont kill.\
\
2: Summon the dragon and back up so you dont get crit in the face right off the bat.\
\
3: If you have a boar, have it charge+growl to generate a lot of aggro.  Immediatly put scorpid sting on because the dragon will hit for over 600, even with 45% reduction.  Keep mend pet up at all times\
\
4: At about 70%, your pet should be rather low on health.  Trap the dragon and keep mend pet up. Once your pet is at full hp, Misdirection, pop all cooldowns+trinkets, and aimed-shot, multi-shot, arcane shot.\
\
5: Keep dps'ing untill your pet is at 25% and trap again.  Keep mend pet up , but this time feign death to wipe your aggro.  Send the pet in, and keep dps'ing.\
\
6: Repeat 5 as many times as you have to until the dragon dies. Congrats on the kill!\
\
Really easy quest to solo, shouldn't be a group quest.  This method may take a while, but its better than having your pet die and lose happiness or taking 10% durability.",
