    "1027429137530291372007/02/01 20:25:48plasmasnakemgIf you're neutral with the Netherwing from the Shadowmoon Valley quest line, make sure to click \"At War\" before you use the item to summon him. It'll put you right in combat, you won't be able to attack him and he'll rip you a new one and you can't click \"At War\" while in combat.\
