    "1090710960221960242007/06/22 22:55:08WirelessConfirmed. Seems that if you have already completed a previous alchemy mastery (Elixir, Potion, Transmutation) you can drop it at the NPC that you finished you mastery quest (eg: Elixir mastery was the bird-person in lower city in shattrath) for 150g the first time (not sure if it goes up, like talent resets.) Then you need to go the the NPC that gives you the mastery of your choice (eg: Transmutation is in netherstorm) and just talk to them. You dont need mats for that quest. I still have my four primal mights.",
