    "109079602450960242007/06/02 14:54:39DytbotAs of patch 2.1.0, when you Unlearn another mastery to take up Transmutation Mastery you do not need to do the quest. By that, you save the 4 Primal Might's you would need to get. Furthermore, all you need to do is go talk with Zarehi (http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=22427). Not like above comments about Thrallmar.\
\
