    "9955211394102113942008/01/02 05:37:37dratejinnThis is also soloable as a 70 enhance shammy, just use ur earth elemental and dps , as the earth elemental gets low on health , heal it ^^ (u may want to take a mana pot with u for if you get low on mana but u can also use ur shamanistic rage to replenish mana)",
