    "1052230568810305682007/02/04 12:06:38marskid2The Cipher of Damnation is an extremely long quest line in Shadowmoon Valley.  It is a prerequisite for attunement to The Eye in Tempest Keep and Mount Hyjal in Caverns of time.  \
