    "104076121940612192007/04/02 17:43:47ElastikI advise warriors to not bother trying to solo Morug. The poison attack can be avoided pretty easily, but the saw blade attack is spammed far too often both to outlast him and to brute-force him in zerker stance. I tried kiting him to the Stormspire, but I could not both damage him enough to get loot and get him to Stormspire without dying. Since you need to be within 30 yds to shoot him every few seconds you will eat a lot of saw blades on the way there. Even if I didn't eat any poison splashes he would have me down at 4-5k hp by the time I got to the Stormspire, and then you need to get him down to 50% (iirc for loot) before you can drag him to the guards. Get a group-mate for this one. \
