    "104076249920624992007/04/05 10:58:33FinnKilled both elites solo as a protection paladin. I judged Wisdom + Seal of Wisdom and wore them down with exorcism and the usual holyshield/ret aura/BoSanctuary. I used my hammer of justice to stun and bandage. \
