    "104076945720694572007/04/19 03:32:04passion4codeSoloed very easily as an arcane / fire mage.  Stacked fire vulnerability (after pyroblast / slow combo for an intro) and flipped arcane power and continued to pummel them down.  Mobs around them where a bit of a hastle, but meh...more loot.",
    "104073286960328692007/02/08 22:53:17KyanaSoloed both as feral druid, in bear form.\
