    "9639103620201036202007/06/13 10:34:48seckidKamsis can be solo'd too if you've downed curator and talked to Gradav.  This actually seemed easier than Gradav.  Not sure if it's because after watching the protectors, i know how to run around em now or if they just stay out of the way for me.\
