  ["When the Cows Come Home69"] = {
    "103376967npcBessy20415npcThadell2046412300",
    "103375175530517552007/03/15 18:00:05KamanoOddly enough, this doesn't work like most escort quests. You can stray as far away from Bessy as you want, and even if you die, you won't fail. I actually got ambushed by 3 mobs at once and died, but Bessy decided to keep moving on while I was fighting, so some of them left her alone. Anyway, I ran back to my corpse and ressed and she was still there and I took down the last mob beating on her and continued on.\
\
Nice little trick, just be real quick about getting back so she doesn't get killed, though as was said, she can take a good beating.\
\
Edit: Actually, now that I think about it, my not failing might have just been pure luck... like Bessy being out of combat when I died or something of that nature.",
    "10337147375101473752007/09/01 00:29:54Szentvery easy for a priest.\
\
just shackle undead and she didn't even agro the mobs for me, just walked past them. By the time shack broke, I was far away and they just went out of combat.\
\
edit: dont forget you can dispel the soulbind",
