    "103376125020612502007/04/02 19:01:33homiebrahShe makes a better hamburger than escort quest.  Always nice when I let the Ally do the mob cleaning.  Only had 2 to deal with, and both were aggroed when she mooed at them.",
    "10337128393101283932007/07/28 20:40:15Vendor12As a 70 mage i found this quest quite easy, only twice did i have to face more than 2 mobs and even then easily disposed of them without dying or losing a great deal of health. I found you could drink/eat along the way so you would always be able to fight multiple targets",
    "103372692220269222007/01/29 05:58:22Kiba1one thing i found is to do it once and if youve failed be quick and restart again and most of the mobs will be allready killed as besy travels on",
    "10337140828101408282007/08/19 21:45:22KayleexJust soloed as a 70 enhance shaman, forgot about rez sickness which didnt come off until about 2/3s of the way thru the escort. Easiest group quest ive ever done ;D",
    "103372515710251572007/01/26 15:01:21SkoobahSolo'd this as a fury warrior.  So if I can do it everyone can.  Bessy can take a lot of hits, more than enough time to bandage then kill the ghosts attacking her.  Just try not to agro too much around her.",
    "1033735666140356662007/02/14 03:51:01humungusTo make this quest available you need to speak to the farmer Thadell and get the quest from him to actually find Bessy.",
    "103375432130543212007/03/20 14:05:42NydraenVery easy to solo as a level 70 combat swords rogue.  Sorry for redundancy, but I will confirm that Bessy can take a lot of hits.  \
\
The 'hardest' group is a 3-man group, if you're struggling, pop a blind on one, let bessy tank one, while you burn down the remaining one. Other than that group, I didn't even come close to being dead.  I used no cooldowns except for cold blood, and even then, I used it only because it was available.\
\
Also worth noting: you can do the \"A Lingering Suspicion\" quest along with this one.",
    "103372900810290082007/02/01 15:06:08parkerReally, really easy as a Rogue. Just stealthed and walked along Bessy, stunlocked the mobs to death when they aggro'd. I only faced single pulls along the way.",
    "10337126817101268172007/07/25 20:00:09DennaceSomething went weird with this quest, I found that if I aggroed she just kept walking... Which.... didnt matter because I could just stay back and kill them, didnt need to worry about how far away I was...",
