    "1054730586730305862007/02/04 12:17:06marskid2The Cipher of Damnation is an extremely long quest line in Shadowmoon Valley.  It is a prerequisite for attunement to The Eye in Tempest Keep and Mount Hyjal in Caverns of time.  \
\"*\" Indicates quests with rewards.\
\
Quest Line\
1[A] - http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10680 - \"The Hand of Gul'Dan\"\
1[H] - http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10681 - \"The Hand of Gul'Dan\"\
