    "10397106670501066702007/06/18 19:47:20asQarneIn case you get lost on the same thing I did; to close the gate in question, you'll need to use the key (right-click on it) on the glowing sphere in the middle of the gate structure. So you never actually activate the whole gate or anything, just the core of it.",
