    "109113093310309332007/02/04 23:39:37oolzerolooI did this as a shadow priest. I just tab-targetted the imps and mind-flayed them one after the other... If one got too close, I casted shadow word: death. It was ridiculously easy once I started doing that. I didn't even have to fire at them with the cannon at all.",
