    "10911169609101696092007/10/16 07:03:09nivansonThis quest was seriously easy as a shadow priest lvl 68. I killed the mobs around the portal and the cannon. Then I took over the cannon and spent each cooldown of the cannon on shooting the portal down. Now the part that made it so easy was that 1 mind flay (2 ticks) was all that was needed for each imp. I couldn't possibly go out of mana or die...",
