    "10935151183101511832007/09/10 06:25:20FoleasThis quest is very easy, Dont need to heal Barada with the beads, just target anything nasty in the room and hit the beads (put them in your action bar for easier use), wait for cool down, rinse and repeat. I found no need to attack any fiends etc with anything other than the beads. Did this with Lvl 60 rogue, used no pots or abilities, completed with 90% health left.",
