    "10977186217101862172007/11/17 08:12:32robotarmsConfirmed bugged. Camera thing didnt help",
    "109779209970920992007/05/28 00:04:03BahamasStasis Chamber is beyond the room of the first boss Pandemonius in Mana-Tombs Heroic. An npc spawns when you open it. Return to Bash'ir Landing to complete quest. Now you need to grind another Mark of the Nexus-King to be able to open the final Stasis Chamber in Nexus-Prince Shaffar's room.",
    "10977165013201650132007/10/09 04:03:10marthrakJust curious...\
