    "98523740750374072007/02/17 07:16:01RorrI had trouble, as a lvl 70 affliction warlock, taking her down solo. He/she is immune to fear and Curse of Exhaustion so I resorted to the suggestion above. I went to Camp Fear and snagged a 67 elite felguard with enslave demon. The fight was trivial after that.",
    "985215723130157232006/12/15 00:58:04enasimaTusker is on the bluff to the Northeast of Oshu'gun(the bluff is actually visable on your map).  Was able to trio this with three level 66's, though it is likely duoable with two level 68's as the quest log says.  She was not snarable or rootable.",
    "9852149663211118062007/09/06 02:29:05ariochivI kited her back to Telaar, and the guards did help out, but unfortunately the first time I lost credit for the kill. The only problem with kiting her is steering clear of the hostile wildlife. The second time I got credit.",
