    "9852128518301285182007/07/29 04:00:29GoldvingI tried this four times as a level 66 Warlock enslaving a 68 Felguard from Camp Fear, to no avail.  The Felguard just didn't stay enslaved long enough despite my having an epic mount and getting to Tusker ASAP.  The closest I got was getting Tusker to 66% before the Felguard released and evade bugged and Tusker owned me.  If you can get it to work, congratulations, but the Felguard just wouldn't stay enslaved long enough even with Curse of Shadow and everything and I'm done damaging my gear from deaths.",
    "9852212679102126792008/01/04 08:13:49dlotsLocks can solo, just go to the forge camp hate/fear and enslave one of the OMG UBER!!! felguards and go kick some ass (curse of shadows makes enslave last it's full time)",
    "985228608380286082007/01/31 22:07:19fufySolo'ed her easily as a warlock, just go to \"forge camp : fear\", enslave a felguard, come back at her spawn & pwn her.",
    "985218728120187282006/12/31 02:34:17codyCouldn't do it as a rogue on my own (70). She hits for an average of 1000 and does a special attack for ~1000 too. She also does a bleed dot. Immune to crippling poison and blind.\
