    "9852177952201779522007/11/02 03:19:23cchiappaJust soloed as a 66 hunter, pretty easy.  Turned growl *off* on my pet, kited with cheetah all the way back to Garadar, just making sure serpent sting was up all the time.  By the time I got there, she was down to about 1/3 health and the guards made quick work of her.  Helped that Horde had control of Halaa, although she moves slowly enough that it would be easy enough to solo on the roads anyhow, with the help of a mana pot.",
