    "1070538598600385982007/02/19 08:15:59SihmmThis is one of Shadowmoon's various \"phat lewt\" quest chains, and starts differently depending on whether you're Aldor (A) or Scryer (S):\
\
[b]Aldors[/b] pick up the line from [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=21402]Anchorite Ceyla[/url] in the Altar of Sha'tar:\
