\
[b]Scyers[/b] get it from [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=21955]Arcanist Thelis[/url] at the Sanctum of Stars:\
1. (S) [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10683][70] Tablets of Baa'ri[/url]\
2. (S) [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10684][70] Oronu the Elder[/url]\
3. (S) [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10685][70] The Ashtongue Corruptors[/url]\
4. (S) [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10686][70] The Warden's Cage[/url]\
\
At this point the chains converge for both factions:\
5. [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10622][70] Proof of Allegiance[/url]\
6. [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10628][70] Akama[/url]\
7. [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10705][70] Seer Udalo (Dungeon)[/url]\
\
Here, you have to venture into the [b]Arcatraz[/b] (which requires a Rogue with 350 lockpicking or somebody to open the door who's completed the [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10262]Arcatraz Key chain[/url], which requires trips to the Mechanar and the Botanica respectively) to the room just before the final boss.  Sadly it's (nearly) impossible to stealth to.  Finding Udalo leads to:\
\
Talk to Akama:\
8. [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10706][70] A Mysterious Portent[/url]\
Kill waves of nonelites, 3 elites and a boss (5-man) on a terrace outside the Black Temple:\
9. [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10707][70] The Ata'mal Terrace[/url]\
