[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=31000]Bloodwarder's Rifle[/url] (gun)\
[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=30984]Spellbreaker's Buckler[/url] (spelldamage shield)\
[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=30999]Ashtongue Blade[/url] (phsyical DPS dagger)\
[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=30943]Verdant Gloves[/url] (feral leather gloves)\
[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=31417]Staff of the Ashtongue Deathsworn[/url] (healing staff)",
