    "1032314242131444552007/08/22 18:01:54blackwolfwxSoloed as a frost mage. After retrying several scenarios attempting to clear all the waves to finish the quest, discovered that it is only necessary to kill the first 4-5 waves attempting to shut down the forge and pulling the rest.\
