\
And lastly, as soon as you pick up the shutdown crystal from the Overlord, start the shutdown. If you wait too long, he *will* spawn on you. Even knowing this in advance, I was only half done drinking post-fight when spawned right on top of me.",
    "10365126940201269402007/07/26 02:31:17BamftSoloable as a warrior. Took me a Healthstone, Arena Grand Master Shield and Shield wall but I lived for two minutes.\
\
Start tanking the initial three mobs for rage, then once three more come run into them and piercing howl, now just run around close to the center of the forge and spam piercing howl, if the mobs daze you face them for a second and then run away again. Use Healthstones/Charged Crystal Focii/Healing Potions as needed.\
