    "10365162958101629582007/10/04 17:23:42tb2508Also solo'd as a Protection Paladin and must agree with Galoheart, it was a riot!  I also had my full tanking gear on before I began.  I had to LoH at about 30sec left and then bubbled when it was complete and ran out without dying.  Didn't even have to pot... :)  \
