    "1036533795171322872007/02/10 21:47:27aasartorCompleted this quest with a Feral Druid and a Frost Mage.  We were not able to kill the mobs faster than they could spawn.  However, the objective of the quest is not to kill all the mobs; rather it's to survive for the 2 minute shutdown period.  We completed the quest, then proceeded to wipe on the 12 mobs we were training around the room :)\
