    "10256206061112014642007/12/23 13:36:07EfflixiI was able to solo this as a level 70 Holy spec priest. I did have to get a few extra buffs from food and potions but i was able to do it. Here was my strat, just dps him down and shield as needed until you get two adds, fear them (boss is unfearable), heal up, and start dps'ing again. Around this point i popped my mana fiend, not because i needed the mana, but for the extra dps (little though it is, every bit helps).\
\
