    "1054130579700305792007/02/04 12:12:17marskid2The Cipher of Damnation is an extremely long quest line in Shadowmoon Valley.  It is a prerequisite for attunement to The Eye in Tempest Keep and Mount Hyjal in Caverns of time.  \
\"*\" Indicates quests with rewards.\
\
Quest Line\
1(A) - http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10680 - \"The Hand of Gul'Dan\"\
