    "99992893540289352007/02/01 12:49:39DuerreSolo'd this part of the quest as a 66 feral druid.  The tinkerers are easy in bear form.  Engineers are not totally hard but if you don't work it right, they might kill you.  The legionaires are prob the most difficult for a feral druid.  Charge them and kill their cannons first, then bash, shift out, entangle root them and heal.  Once healed, just let the root take it's corse so that bash can cool down.  Then go back in for more.  Tank, bash, root, heal...  takes some time but works like a charm.  Keep some health potions on hand to use incase bash is dodged, blocked, parried, etc.  You should be ok. ;-)",
