\
No special abilities on Skulloc that we noticed, just tank & spank.  The only danger is being down on health/mana from the prelude event.\
\
In the event that some other group thinks they're going to scrooge you by tapping skulloc before you're ready, no fears.  The object dropped can be looted by anyone after he's dead.",
