    "11071130026101300262007/07/31 19:31:29VorphDragonmaw race quests are the most entertaining quests I've completed by far. I have not yet managed to beat Skyshatter but just an advice, when you got aggravated, stop trying to do the quest for a while, because it takes all the fun part and since you get more distracted when you get angry, you wont be able to do quest therefore wasting a huge amount of time. This quest requires a good connection, a good memory, good control over your mouse and keyboard and preferably a riding crop :), nothing else.\
