    "1107117520911891582007/10/26 14:11:22AundoraI stayed above him to his left and cut corners. I also stayed ahead of him at certain times during the same flight. He is very easy once you know what to do and practice a little bit. Did on Pally, so Crusader Aura helped a ton. Only took me about 7 tries, and def go naked.",
    "11071116702201167022007/07/06 21:12:01ArmageddaBasically the best way to do this is to take the very popular strategy from Mulverick (staying right on top of him) and doing one better to stay above and ahead of Skyshatter.\
\
