    "10519305671940305672007/02/04 12:05:48marskid2The Cipher of Damnation is an extremely long quest line in Shadowmoon Valley.  It is a prerequisite for attunement to The Eye in Tempest Keep and Mount Hyjal in Caverns of time.  \
