- Rain of fel flames: long cooldown and uses a reagent (probably a charged crystal focus)... tooltip says something like \"float in the air and destroy all the enemies\"... used it while surrounded by mobs but didn't worked (can't even remember if I had the reagent in bags)... dunno if it has to be used during the jump (will try tomorrow).\
\
I dunno what's the point you need to achieve... probably simply kill all enemies.\
The thing is damn funny... can't really w8 to have another chance (tried 3 times by now)!",
