Combat Sword Rogue (http://armory.worldofwarcraft.com/character-sheet.xml?r=Lightbringer&n=Xyana), \
Feral Druid, \
Marksman Hunter (http://armory.worldofwarcraft.com/character-sheet.xml?r=Lightbringer&n=Novus), \
Retribution Pally.\
\
2 useful tips:  \
\
1. Meatshield + Bear = 7 sec aggro lead for both Bosses.  Bear initializes aggro managment. Meatshield stays high on threat.\
2. Dps stay on angles behind the boss for both fights.  Use cooldowns @ 75% of both fights.  Repeat as available.\
\
2 must-do procedures:\
\
1. Salvation on all dps players, except for fury warrior.  All players must be focused on watching & stopping the castings of both bosses - aka: interrupt/stun/kick/etc.\
