    "9524165918301659182007/10/11 09:09:05sheeshThis quest is basically a harder version of the quest [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10884]Trial of the Naaru: Mercy[/url].\
\
Upon starting the event in the Gauntlet of Flame (correct me if that's not the right name of the place), with the boss and the two archers at the end, you will receive a 50 minute [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=39288]debuff[/url], indicating how long you have to complete the quest. (very similar to [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=27861]The Baron's Ultimatum[/url] in [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?zone=2017]Stratholme[/url]) Even though the debuff will be gone if you die, this does not mean that the quest failed.\
\
