    "106367561510756152007/04/30 16:24:36seyekJust wanted to clarify how this quest works:\
\
Around the Hand of Guldan, there is a road visible from your map that completely circles it. On this road, 3 ghosts ride in a group at 160% speed in a counter-clockwise fashion. So, the best method to find them would be to follow the road in a clockwise direction to head them off. They are 3 non-elite mobs. However, you will get your Truncheon from the first kill. So, if you cannot normally take on 3 at once, attack and kill at least one, then run from the others (preferably on the road so you don't aggro more mobs) after slowing them.  After a short period of running, the mobs chasing you will stand still and evade. Then, you are free to go back and loot your Truncheon. Like all ghosts, hunter traps don't affect them.",
