    "108816522810652282007/04/10 22:28:23JaylenThe respawn rate isn't too much different than on the surface, but perhaps it was fixed to the rate I am reporting currently.  Many early reports on respawn were due to the rate being higher than intended to make up for the high quantity of people entering the zones all at once at the very beginning.  Currently a single person can clear out a wing of the Shadow Tomb, loot and be about halfway through the other side before the first respawn begins appearing.  So I guess it is quick, but not insanely fast.\
