    "109929059820905982007/05/25 21:24:48GahlokAn easier way would be bringing along a mage (party). As feral I rooted, healed and de-poison while the mage was nuking him. My mage said he got an 8k arcane blast or something hit on the mob. He died in less than a minute (or around there).",
