    "1068017068npcEarthmender Sophurus21937npcEarthmender Torlok210243150110681110680210458310480410481510513610514710515810519",
    "10680116531501165312007/07/06 14:03:17killahxxxAs of 2.1 attunement to the Eye is no longer required.",
    "106802878420287842007/02/01 08:11:07Kiba1this quest starts at Earthmender Splinthoof 28, 65",
    "1068028567410285672007/01/31 20:32:291dsk1- The Cipher of Damnation ( 5 man )\
Use the Cipher of Damnation at the Altar of Damnation to summon Cyrukh the Firelord.\
Destroy Cyrukh the Firelord and then speak with Earthmender Torlok, also found at the Altar of Damnation.\
=> Use the stone of damnation head at (45,46) (the place you started with the purple aura). Using the stone at the altar will spawn the boss, and the 3 Sons will fly in to help. Talk to them when ready and they will begin the fight.\
NOTE: These 3 sons will tank the boss pretty well as long as you dont pull aggro to early. The boss is a straight forward fight. You basically need to do 300k damage in a few minutes before the NPC's die, otherwise you'll end up tanking. Can be done with a decent 5man group\
\
After you finish this quest go talk to khadgar in Shattrath. He will tell you to talk to the Naaru in the center of Shattrath. This then leads to these three quests:\
\
- Trial of the Naaru: Mercy\
A'dal in Shattrath City wants you to recover the Unused Axe of the Executioner from the Shattered Halls of Hellfire Citadel.\
This quest must be completed in Heroic dungeon difficulty.\
=> Obtained from Kargath Bladefist in the Shattered Halls.\
\
- Trial of the Naaru: Strength\
A'dal in Shattrath City wants you to recover Kalithresh's Trident and Murmur's Essence.\
This quest must be completed in Heroic dungeon difficulty.\
=> Obtained from Warlord Kalithresh in Coilfang Steamvaults.\
\
- Trial of the Naaru: Tenacity\
A'dal in Shattrath City wants you to rescue Millhouse Manastorm from the Arcatraz of Tempest Keep.\
This quest must be completed in Heroic dungeon difficulty.\
=> Rescue Millhouse Manastorm from Arcatraz\
\
Return to Khadgar to finnish your attunement.\
\
Heroic Mode: To put any of the Tempest Keep instances in Heroic Mode, you must be Revered with the Sha'tar. The key can be purchased from the quartermaster in Shattrath City, Terokkar Forest.\
\
GOOD LUCK & HF :)",
    "1068017123931283562007/10/18 16:07:12unitepunxTempest Keep no longer needs Attunment to enter, however for the few that actually did so they will gain a special name title \"Champion of the Naaru\" in patch 2.3.",
