    "10408202008111756692007/12/15 20:12:03PerilousPwnerAt first it bugged and he killed us (I had done 2 powerfield and someone else did 1 powerfield) then I did what someone mentioned above, and made 1 person do all the powerfields (not 1 each, one person did all 3) and it worked like a charm.",
