    "104434462331255562007/03/01 14:31:22xelepartThere's lots of quests that say \"go see <npc name>, they have a quest for you.\"  Most of these aren't necessary, though, as you can get the followon without doing the \"go see the person.\"  So once you do Demonic Contamination, you are no longer eligable for Helping the Cenarion Post, 'cause the quest they are telling you to do is no longer available to you.\
