    "10898193233411837652007/11/29 07:15:56Mag1tekI've found a workaround for this bug. Before starting the quest, head to the platform that Skywing jumps down to and kill the two mobs there. Then immediately head back to Skywing and start the quest so that those mobs don't respawn by the time Skywing makes his way to that point. \
\
