    "110158810350881032007/05/23 06:34:22ElastikThese can be farmed very nicely in the mine below the Dragonmaw encampment (entrance southeast of the camp) on Netherwing ledge. There were lots of mobs in there and it was not as heavily farmed as the surface above.",
    "11015139442111187342007/08/17 08:36:01barfieldThis quest will take a lot of time doing but drops alone will net you about 10 gold in grey items.",
    "11015206089102060892007/12/23 14:53:33oldmanbootzzWhat I did for this quest was actually spend the time killing the mobs waiting for me to get 40 until I unlocked more dailies, mainly the ones in the mine.  All of the mobs in there drop crystals, so about every other day I had enough crystals to turn in the quest.  Between the races and finding eggs, there was no reason to farm for these when you could be doing something to get more money/rep.  If you look up netherwing eggs on youtube, there are several videos that can help you to find eggs that are far easier to get and net almost the same rep, or way more when you find 8-12 a day as I sometimes do.",
    "110151187341801187342007/07/10 19:04:26KathuckaBloody hell....  At a roughly 33% drop rate, this quest will require mindlessly grinding out an average of 120 kills...and since it is a \"collect X bear asses\" style quest, you can't speed it up by grouping.\
\
You'd better really really want that shiny dragon mount if you want to work hard enough to turn this one in every day.  Otherwise, just turn it in less frequently than daily, as you get the crystals from your other activities on the ledge.",
