    "1066740410470404102007/02/22 08:20:15marskid2The Illidari-Bane questline is a series of quests that leads to some cool anti-demon weapons.  It involves entering many level-70 instances, so you probably want to do the prerequisites before then.  David Wayne is also rumored to be Mograine of the Ashbringer.  \
\
Quest Line\
1 - http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10621 - Illidari-Bane Shard - Drops from Overseer Ripsaw.\
2 - http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10626 - Capture the Weapons - Soloable as a warlock with banish.\
3[A] - http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10662 - The Hermit Smith\
3[H] - http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10663 - The Hermit Smith\
4 - http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10664 - Additional Materials\
\
After returning Additional Materials, he offers you two quests which can be completed in any order.\
5 - http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10665 - Fresh From the Mechanar - The Mechanar in Tempest Keep\
6 - http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10666 - The Lexicon Demonica - Shadow Labyrinth in Auchindoun\
\
