7 - http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10670 - Tear of the Earthmother - Shattered Halls in Hellfire Citadel\
8 - http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10667 - Underworld Loam - The Steamvault in Coilfang Reservoir\
\
After finishing all these, you can get your new weapon!\
9 - http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10676 - Bane of the Illidari\
10 - http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10679 - Quenching the Blade\
