    "10583183087101830872007/11/12 19:38:07relentlassThe quest is hard to solo, period. I did it quickly with a 70 mage and 70 lock. I died a few times trying to solo as a 70 lock. Just too many mobs and tinkerers are damned hard to solo in cloth as affliction.\
