    "105832512420251242007/01/26 14:05:02nekokiAfter heading down the ramp, he is on the top floor in the very far back on the ground.",
    "105839618811840322007/06/02 21:55:20Samsaraim having an issue where the new change to targetting and LOS targets conflict with each other and they prevent me from targetting Flanis to talk to him. After doing /target Flanis i was able to target him but could not \"talk\" to him. Anyone else encounter the same issue?",
