    "105835834620583462007/03/27 22:56:05thunderlordroanThis quest can be annoying for a firemage. There are infernals along the way that are immune to fire, beware. Other than that, it's a relatively easy quest.",
    "10583123406101234062007/07/19 14:10:32AstaEasy as a lvl 70 feral druid. Going in was no problem. Going out I tried to do it the easy way and hit Dash while prowling. Unfortunately, I passed too close by a dormant infernal and got hit by fire which broke stealth. I almost made it to the entrance though.. :P",
