However, this is coming from a mage, im not sure how easy it is to stealth to that room in the first place.\
\
And remember, this is only a suggestion, not 100% sure you'll be able to stealth to the room of Blackheart easily, even at all.",
    "10091198856101988562007/12/10 02:18:38dodsfallasoloed as a 69 rogue, just went into the room, went to the tent on the right, sapped the closest mob and sidestepped making sure i could still open the object, got both, got myself killed reset the instance and repeated",
