    "10516159249901592492007/09/27 07:16:55PhoepsUseful Information for patch 2.2:\
\
As of Patch WoW patch 2.2 you can't pull the boss away from his elite bodyguards the usual way anymore using a weapon pull, this will make his bodyguards come for you.\
OBS! As it might have been mentioned in above comments however, you can still use the \"Bloodmaul Brutebane Kegs\" to lure the ogres out - this includes him! \
\
How to:\
\
Kill the front 2 guards, usually a brute and a shaman - these can be pulled one by one and is easy to kill. Next go exactly far enough in to stand halfway between the bonfire and the entrance, inside the room, plant a \"Brutemaul Brutebane Keg Brew\" on the floor and back up. The Boss will react immidiatly but if its too far away he won't notice. If u accedently place it to far away wait for the CD and try place one closer in. Once he reaches the brew you can freely pull and kill him without having to deal with his bodyguards!\
Remember! - It might be adviseable to bring more then 2 brews incase u accedently place one wrong, and its annoying having to run out and find anther in the middle of the quest!\
\
