    "11086153178211186802007/09/15 02:35:07vexis58As a holy priest, I kill these things slowly enough that the first one respawns by the time I'm done killing the last. I never get more than one aggroing, these mobs have a surprisingly low aggro radius. No danger of pulling any of the nearby elites either. Perfect spot to get all 20 kills for any ranged class.\
