    "106578020730802072007/05/09 05:29:05GarnockI did this quest as a lvl 69 Demonology Warlock. And i found out a little trick for lock's to make it a little more easy and faster. When you see a Scalewing Serpent use the ''Shield'' and let the Serpent shoot Lightning strike on you. And then fear him with Fear rank 1! (Only last 10 sec's) So when the fear break's he will almost immediately shoot a Lightning strike on you. And then just repeat with Fear (Rank 1 ^^)  =)",
