    "1065711519111260912007/07/03 20:25:20skywyzeSince you can't always predict when they're going to shoot lightning, or have perfect control over aggro, I found it a lot easier to simply lay down a freezing trap at about 25 yards, shoot once (it'll fire lightning right away, so long as you're within its range) and run away. Wait for the trap to dissipate on its own. Concussive Shot it to force it to attack you with lightning again. Lay down a new freezing trap when it reaches you. Move away. Etc.\
\
