    "10689156128501561282007/09/21 09:49:27SihmmThis is part of the [b]Scryer[/b] version of the [b]Book of Fel Names[/b] chain.  As well as reputation with your chosen faction, if you complete it you can choose from:\
[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=31013]Ceremonial Kris[/url] (+heal dagger)\
[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=31010]Slayer's Axe[/url] (2H +str axe)\
[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=30948]Sunfury Legguards[/url] (+AP mail pants)\
[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=30933]Hauberk of Karabor[/url] (+AP leather chest)\
[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=31002]Summoner's Blade[/url] (+dmg sword)\
[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=31009]Wildcaller[/url] (feral staff)\
\
As with the [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10707]Medallion of Karabor[/url] line, this chain starts different depending on whether you're Aldor (A) or Scryer (S).  All the quests are rated level 70 - though the chain is available at level 68, it sends you to the [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?zone=3789]Shadow Labyrinth[/url] to kill [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=18667]Blackheart[/url], which you might want to hold off on until level 70.\
\
[b]Aldors[/b] pick it up from [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=21860]Exarch Onaala[/url] at the Altar of Sha'tar:\
1. (A) [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10587]Karabor Training Grounds[/url]\
2. (A) [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10637]A Necessary Distraction[/url]\
3. (A) [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10640]Altruis[/url]\
\
[b]Scryers[/b] need to visit [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=21954]Larissa Sunstrike[/url] at the Sanctum of the Stars:\
1. (S) [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10687]Karabor Training Grounds[/url]\
2. (S) [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10688]A Necessary Distraction[/url]\
3. (S) [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10689]Altruis[/url]\
\
Here the chains converge on your old friend [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=18417]Altruis the Sufferer[/url] in Nagrand.  He gives out three quests that need to be completed (in any order) before you can continue:\
4a. [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10641]Against the Legion[/url] - Netherstorm\
4b. [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10668]Against the Illidari[/url] - Shadowmoon Valley\
4c. [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10669]Against All Odds[/url] - Zangarmarsh\
Having gone around the world killing stuff, you can now return to Altruis and receive:\
5. [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10646]Illidan's Pupil[/url]\
which leads directly into\
6. [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10649]The Book of Fel Names[/url]\
\
Now it's time for a venture into the Shadow Labyrinth to kill [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=18667]Blackheart[/url]!  Once that's done that and his body has been looted for the book, it's back to Altruis where again the chains diverge depending on your allegiance.\
\
[b]Aldor[/b]:\
7. (A) [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10650]Return to the Aldor[/url] - back to Altar of Sha'tar\
8. (A) [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10651]Varedis Must Be Stopped[/url]\
\
[b]Scryer[/b]:\
7. (S) [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10691]Return to the Scryers[/url] - back to Sanctum of Stars\
8. (S) [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10692]Varedis Must Be Stopped[/url]\
\
Varedis Must Be Stopped is the final part.  It's a 5-man group quest that sends you to the terrace outside the Black Temple to kill four elites: [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=21178]Varedis[/url], [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=21164]Netharel[/url], [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=21168]Theras[/url] and [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=21171]Alandien[/url].  Look them up  for co-ordinates and tips on killing them - they're pretty straightforward, really.\
\
When they're dead it's a simple matter of returning to the questgiver to choose a prize.",
