    "1058838573130385732007/02/19 07:40:05SihmmCyrukh's primary attacks are physical, meaning they can be mitigated by armor.  With 20k armor, he was hitting for between 600 and 1300.  He also has a ~1.2k knock away that reduces aggro on the target knocked away, and a ~3k trample that hits anyone in melee range.  His final ability is a targeted AoE ignite (fire-based) that ignites an area of ground around a player.  The AoE damage can be minimised by spreading out so only one person gets hit at a time, and by moving quickly out of the ignited area when it does hit.\
\
In my experience, having a well-geared tank hold aggro on him is far more reliable than trying to let the NPCs tank him.  It was also my experience that losing aggro to a knock-away caused Cyrukh to focus on one of the NPCs rather than my group mates, but don't rely on it!",
    "10588248752150248752007/01/26 07:11:03CombineYou start the quest near 42,45.\
\
1. Use totems on the fire and earth elementals surrounding the immediate area.\
2. Use totems on air elementals near Netherwing Fields. 62,57\
3. Use totems on water elementals near 47,22\
\
Then you go up north to talk to the NPC.  54,23\
\
He then asks you to use a whistle on whipper tubers.  Note:  A boar must be alive and near for it to work.  They tubers are around 52,20\
\
Then He asks you to destroy some eggs,  They are just north of him down the cliff.\
\
Once you have done those two quests he will ask you to find his 3 Sons.\
\
The sons are located...\
 \
\
Artor: 30,50\
Will ask you to slay the main mistress which is up the stairs and to the right.  Then you will have to grind those demons to find a quest item.  Then you will have to escort a NPC up the hill.  Once up the hill the NPC will summon a non elite you must kill.   Loot that mob and your 1/3rd done.\
\
Gromtor: 45,24\
Talk to him and he will ask you to find something.  The item you need is locked randomly in a chest that the naga hold.  Go kill some naga and they will randomly drop keys.  Open the chests and eventually youll get the quest item.\
\
Borak: 47,57\
Asks you to do a multitude of things.  The confusing ones involve finding an egg.  Which there are some located in the bird people village just near the NPC.  It will take quite some tries to find the correct one.  He should then ask you to bring it to someone in Shattarah.  \
Also you will end up having to kill some blood elves Eclipse point for armor scraps.  Then you will use a Blood ELf disguise to infiltrate the camp.  Talk to the big guy at the back of camp.  Careful the firehawk beasts see threw the disguise and if you get knocked out of it you must return to the SOn to get a new costume.\
\
Then he will ask you to kill an Elite.  This elite is 61 and can be killed with a tank, healer, and dps.  Once you kill this Dual Thunderfury badass you fight his pet.  Although the item you need is on the guy.\
\
After killing this guy return to the son.  Then return with all 3 of the quests completed to the father at 54,23. \
Rewards from this part are:\
\
http://www.wowhead.com/?item=30951\
http://www.wowhead.com/?item=30939\
http://www.wowhead.com/?item=30967\
http://www.wowhead.com/?item=30962\
http://www.wowhead.com/?item=30925\
http://www.wowhead.com/?item=30944\
\
He will then tell you to fight the big green golemagg. \
\
