    "9385194416201944162007/12/01 12:53:47devarimWhile the Skitterers are pretty much useless...they do have a small purpose...I had the quest Ravager Egg roundup from Legassi at the crashed zeppelin, and I got 3 or 4 of the eggs from the skitterers. \
