    "93852604140260412007/01/27 23:01:54AvendhrasNote that there are two types of ravager near Falcon's Watch -- the quillfang ravager and the quillfang skitterer. You do not receive credit for killing the skitterers, which is unfortunate because they outnumber the ravagers by a pretty healthy margin, and they are very fast, and very aggressive. Also, they're colored differently than the ravagers -- they're mostly blue while the ravagers are a uniform drab green.\
