    "99623416941285842007/02/11 15:50:58kjpodsiaTo clarify the above complaint, the problem is that once a group starts a leg of this quest line, Gurgthock stops accepting both new quests *and* turn-ins of completed quests.  So even after you beat Mogor, you may end up having to stand around for a while before you can claim your prize.\
