    "10816205474102054742007/12/22 09:16:57geordiesiObviously easier with a flying mount as are most q's but to some extent this works without too,    find a corner such as 68.1 36.5, there will be 2 slayers fighting, a darkweaver doing his stuff and a chosen patroling and taking in the corner as part of his patrol. The eyes and the drakonids will not notice you in the corner.  Kill the slayers, and the chosen when he comes to you, fitting in a well timed visit to the darkweaver. Repeat as necessary. Couldn't be easier. Don't forget to visit the building over the wall to get Smith Gorlunk at 67.6 36.0 for Primed Key Mold Quest Item for Hellfire Citadel.",
