    "10816171793101717932007/10/19 14:32:17VerdiceDied 6 times doing this quest as a 70 feral druid, had a hell of a time.\
\
I developed a strategy for each of the mobs:\
\
Slayers) Pull them one-by-one at the front gate, or Cyclone them, shift into cat form, wait for your energy to build, then take them on. Usually respawns come so you don't have to hunt around for all 8. Of course, watch for the 70 elite. Mangled them up, rake 'em for DoT, and then ferocious bite for a kill. Found out this was much easier than just straight Mangle-Ferocious Bite combo.\
\
Darkweavers) Easy to kill, just fly to a ledge where you see one and make sure they aren't charging a champion at the time. Pounce, mangle, mangle, bite, dead. Keep in mind there are some in corners that sitting and aren't doing anything. If a Champion aggros you, get your back away from the ledge! He'll send you flying over and then you'll aggro elites and slayers below.\
