    "108169871910987192007/06/05 14:01:41DunedainAnother good location is around 69, 35 - on the landing leading up the steps to the top of the dias. You can drop in the corner against the rock wall and kill the two Chosen on the landing, then the two Chosen at the bottom of the landing, then pull Darkweavers from the surrounding area. We did have one elite Drakonid wander up there, but the two of us (70 holy priest and 70 MM hunter) were able to kill it without much problem. \
