    "10248107571101075712007/06/20 00:25:08MarudasI did this quest last night (6/20) with a hunter helping me. I took control of the Scrap Reaver (Holy Paladin) while the hunter did DPS. Overall not a difficult thing, Smash (The aggro/damage ability) is very nice to use at the start of the fight, at least a few times to build up aggro. However, i dont think Slam is as useless as some people make it out to be. To ease the pain of healing this robot, I used the slam to interupt Negatron's channeled ability, Earthquake. It seemed to help.\
