    "10248126861301268612007/07/25 22:41:36kaoethielFrost Mage - Soloed... Kinda lol.  Others may try Tho using my same Dynamics.\
\
Materials Needed: Swiftness Potion.\
\
*Note: I'd say health potion but the swiftness pot kills the CD. <3\
\
Start the quest, When u start it, throw up frost shield... Back up to the torch right next to the road.  Then spam ur pet attack button so that ur pet moves to Negatron the second he pops aggressive.  Let the pet smack him a bit, then using Ice Lance, you hit em once or twice.  \
\
*Note:  Ice Lance is a low DPS insta cast spell, I use it to create LOW hate.  You'll see why in a minute.\
\
Then stun negatron with the pet, and start bookin towards Area 52.  Make sure, however, you make sure to ice lance when u think you might deagro the guy.   To assist with that, JUST to make sure, I pulled out my water elemental.  Also, if negatron got too close early, since my ice lances are so low DPS, and my pets hit pretty hard, my pet would pull him in the opposite direction giving me more head start.  Between your travels from the initiating the quest, to Area 52, you'll notice negatron is one fast motha fu<ka.  So when u think hes getting  kinda close for comfort, pop that swiftness pot.  It will put u to a running speed, I thought, was the same speed (%50) or a TINY bit faster... I don't know, I didn't care... He was fast, so i got fast.  \
\
Upon entering the town, you are NOT out of the clear.  The guards who are \"Agents\" as the last part of their names, will NOT help you... So don't hang out around them thinking they will... It is the Brusiers that run in to smack megatron. SO, I ran through the doorway closest to the Gryphon master (Still had swiftness up) Forward, then taking an immediate left across the bridge that heads to the engineering supplier, agroing the brusiers around me... (CONTINUE  ICE LANCING AS NEEDED, YOU CAN LOSE AGRO EVEN WITH BRUISERS BASHING HIM!) Then i continued into almost a square by taking a right running to the other bridge. \
\
**Note Somewhere in town between the agroing the guards and going across the OTHER bridge  to the inn, i Ice blocked... When i ice blocked, I allowed the bruisers to get agro, so i stayed Blocked the full duration**\
\
Now if you're lucky, as I was, Allies AND horde in town see this going on and are like \"DAMN I WANT TO KILLZ THE BOT!!!!\"  And help you out...If not, well, you got cold snap, Ice barrier, and Ice block with the water elemental for a short distraction to keep ya goin.  Just keep agroing all the bruisers u can, cus he swats em down.  GL\
\
*NOTE: Used Ice Lance btw if you didnt catch it, because it does low dps, and causes the lowest amount of threat while i was moving, needed to make it easy for the guards to pull hate off me.*",
