    "10248188567101885672007/11/20 21:10:50TuhaTomI was pretty disappointed as well to see the heal button missing now... I have done this quest twice on other toons in the past, and thought I was having UI troubles until I checked wowhead here and saw that it was changed in a recent patch.\
