    "102481248771154682007/07/22 06:47:19dunravenI solo'd this quest (without repair ability) as a 70 Paladin. If you are a healer with reasonably good gear, you should be able to do the same. Put scrap reaver on the boss and run to about 30 yard range, where you will be out of range of the earthquake and charge abilities, then spam heals on the scrap reaver.\
\
Make sure to deal some damage to the boss so you get kill credit, and use your scrap reaver's smash ability every cooldown as it is your primary damage. It will be a long fight but very doable as any healing class.\
