    "11001113816201138162007/07/01 10:58:12DraconaxJust did this fight last night for my epic flight form.  Was actually quite easy after the recent retuning on the fight.  Had myself, feral druid tank, rogue, elem shaman, and a mage.  I made macros to regrowth each statue, which made things MUCH easier imo.  I would simply toss some hots on the tank, do a round on each statue, then head back to the tank for 20 seconds.  I find it much simpler to use regrowth over rejuv, because of the extra 9 seconds.  The banish phase seemed very simple, I barely saw anyone's health move at all during the time, even the aoeing mage.  Also note that the spellbomb is now a curse and can be removed, which is a huge help as well.",
