    "1030913986931706342007/08/18 03:46:56KnoxpwnsThe constant crits aren't a bug. With phyiscal damage, anything you attack that is sitting or lying down is an automatic crit. seeing as this mob is lying, and it dont get up, all your attacks will be crits until it stands. Lucky for you, it don't stand, so you get the nice DPS increase.",
