\
When my elemental was at about 25% health and I figured he would lose the battle alone, I helped him finish off that first mob, then continued DPS on the reaver, with him helping. Second mob comes, I sheep him. Continued DPS. Third mob comes, put water elemental on him.\
\
By the time the fourth came, the reaver was pretty low, maybe around 20% max, and I was near full health. Right behind the fourth came the fifth, sixth and seventh mobs, so I just kept ice barrier'ing and frost nova'ing to give me time to finish off the reaver.\
\
