    "103159821611600512007/06/04 18:13:43bronNot too bad of a quest; concentrate on the Nethermancers, as their adds will die when they do. Clear the sister patrol as she comes around and you should be fine. Respawn was fairly quick. Hardest part of the quest was dealing with the bloodfuries as i came over the bridge. The fairly good signet drop is another plus on this quest.",
