    "103156621231453012007/04/12 18:17:05macallanThis was an easy solo for a general spec 68 rogue. Do it with \"A dark pact\". Go right into the Forge Ara building, you will see the overseer patrolling. His patrol time gives you adequate time to kill one of the four nethermancers arranged around the center. They don't add from their position closest to the center; wait for the overseer to pass, kill, heal, stealth. Move around the circle. You can easily kill the overseer in his patrol when he goes into his own room, but he re-gens quickly so be careful. After the first four, go outside and kill the Tinkers and Masters, (pull the first with a ranged throw or shot to the edge of the cliff), then kill the other two as you will. Cycle back inside for four more nethermancers, rinse and repeat.  For the sister in the dark pact, I killed one on the way up, and then the same one twice on the way down.  First kill one of the nethermancers by the cart near the cliff wall (pull here with a ranged shot to avoid her partner). Then wait for the sister to patrol. Easy kills if you don't miss your kick or KS to interupt their casts.",
