    "10634116024101160242007/07/05 14:09:10MirandaTook him out yesterday in a group of 5.  Coords for mountain peak at 69.8, 85.9 are great, but we had to clear the flayers on the nearby clearing (including a 72 Elite) before we could get him.  I'm a shadow priest and stood on the peak while group waited below on the clearing.  As he flew by, I threw a SWP dot on him and levitated down to group to pull him down.  Easy fight.  Two shadow priests with VE kept everyone healed.  Only problem is that the Elite flayer respawns very quickly, but she's easy and you can easily take both at the same time.  Toughest part was getting him out of the air.",
