    "1085433796180337962007/02/10 21:49:02CryogenicistThe drakes are around the 68,60 area. The crystal can't be used if you are in combat. If you use the crystal and there are more orcs around the drake, it will aggro those orcs, so you need to kill them all before the quest will accept the drake as being freed. Kill orcs around the drake that aren't linked to it before using the crystal if you can. I also had a bug where the drake simply ran across the entire orc camp after I used the crystal. It aggroed all of the orcs, who killed the drake at the end of the camp, and then came to kill me afterwards. Be ready to run out of the camp if this happens.",
