    "11097179714101797142007/11/05 17:37:11NinaEasily soloed as a restoration shaman. Any gear could do it I guess but I dont even find it challenging. I got full t4 and other various stuff, I guess it helps a bit. But i think any resto shammy can do it. Just keep Healing Stream Totem & earthshield up on yourself while chainhealing the NPC's and you will complete the Q within 3-5 mins or whatever it is, very easy :) U may have to pop one super mana pot and one mana-tide tho, but its worth the effort :)",
    "1109793455100934552007/05/30 05:42:34BSChimI soloed this as a Priest (as Scryers) I just spammed Greater Heal and fought for aggro, once I succeeded in that I ran straight to the grphyon master and kept myself up.\
