    "11097196742101967422007/12/06 03:03:32DirewolfXYou can also run behind one of the Scryer buildings to get out of combat and eat/drink.  I think as long as the defenders don't die and you don't go too far away, you won't fail the quest.  I used this trick to solo the quest as a mage.",
    "11097147088811353402007/08/31 10:34:52adashielMost who choose to do [i]this[/i] quest are still grinding reputation, but that's not true for daily questers in general.  For those of us who are already Exalted and are looking for quests to fill out our daily quota, knowing exactly how much each rewards is invaluable.  From the perspective of someone who will receive no reputation, this quest has a poor risk-reward value.",
