    "11101145331101453312007/08/28 07:58:31RanaA complete and total nightmare of a quest as a rogue. The Skybreakers are immune to stuns, and you cannot show your face without getting aggro from a least a few, even if you're just standing there. To make things worse, half the mobs are unreachable (too high), and since we're melee, unlike all the NPC's, we have no choice but to stand in the front where the newly spawned mobs see us first and aggro. \
