    "106511561241001561242007/09/21 09:44:40SihmmThis is the conclusion to the [b]Aldor[/b] version of the [b]Book of Fel Names[/b] chain, which gives Aldor/Scryer rep as well as some nice blue rewards.  If you complete it, you can choose from:\
