For this you must speak with A'dal in Shattrath city.\
5. http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10949 [70] Entry into the Black Temple\
For this, just speak with the naaru Xi'ri in front of Black Temple.\
6. http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10985 [70] A Distraction for Akama\
Unknown what this quest asks of you, most likely you need to defend Xi'ri and make your way into Black Temple. At the end, you become attuned to enter and are granted The Medallion of Karabor (http://www.wowhead.com/?item=32649)\
\
At this point, you are attuned and can enter Black Temple, although the chain continues and you can soon upgrade your medallion. It continues with:\
