    "11090211055111945632008/01/01 15:05:29sushibarThe top-of-portal trick worked perfectly for me,  Just moved back enough so the beam went through the edge,.  Didn't take one hit.  I lost contact once, had to fly out and start it going again.  Just a minute or two of waiting for him to get drained and walk into the portal.  Easiest 500 rep I ever made..",
    "1109017861411952162007/11/03 15:45:13retrofadeThis worked for me as well; however, the first time that I tried it, the Soul Cannon was only hitting him for ~500 damage a tick instead of ~2,000. So I had to fly away, and then wait for him to pat around and get back in range again. When I tried it the second time, it was hitting him for ~2,000 a tick. He also walks away at about 5%, so you need to follow him to keep the beam on him while he goes to the portal.",
    "1109093877161905752007/05/30 19:51:44graymouserHerbalists should scout the area for a dreaming glory before taking him on.  that buff alone had me nearly at full at the end of the fight.",
    "1109095216220952162007/06/01 08:42:55ShalafeinEasiest way to do this quest after it took me about 4 maybe 5 tries to do it is to wait until hes is close to the portal. Activate the cannon and hide behind the pillar ( i found the right side if your behind the portal to be the easiest one to use) Make sure you have LOS on him or your be subject to his attacks. He will stand there while you drain him and you wont take damage. But you have to make sure  LOS is the issue the cannon will still work however",
    "11090198485111945632007/12/09 11:24:25SilentwonThis one worked for me.  Just mounted, pressed UP and then attacked him, pressed the \"e\" to move slightly then landed.  kept attacking and voila, 11g 99s\
