    "11090201872102018722007/12/15 15:59:44catcovFor warlocks - demon armor is perfect here to help (very slightly) with the shadowbolts.",
    "110901137931301137932007/07/01 10:03:26SilentKnifeA little confusing, at first. Tried the \"fly around him in circles\" method to no avail. Tried the \"hang out above the portal\" method....again, to no avail. Hit him with the beam when he's right in front of the portal, then fly back through the portal and hide behind the right hand pillar of the portal. Try not to break LOS, and if in the right position, you'll take no damage what-so-ever. I posted a screenshot of my position....worked like a charm once i figured out the correct positioning!",
    "11090143026101430262007/08/23 18:57:24holmcrossI went behind the Portal as the screen shot suggested, and he simply chain casted cripple which never hit me. He did not go into Evade, and he didn't advance on me and attack. Easy as pie.",
    "110908955540895552007/05/24 13:05:37SlystalIf you have more than 6k health, the shadowbolts alone WONT kill you.  They are just there to scare you.  However, dont get too close or else he will punch you and that is what can screw you.",
    "1109089185240891852007/05/24 05:34:04LastemperorReally easy one. Drain his health down while you are in the air with your flying mount. Avoid meteors/fireballs. \
