    "11008201923212011452007/12/15 17:45:07RandomixxYou have to fly around Skettis on your flying mount and drop bombs on the groups of eggs which can be found on top of the buildings. It is a bit like the bombing run quests in Hellfire Peninsula (The two Gateways Murketh and Shaadraz, as well as the Abyssal Shelf) except that you do it from your own flying mount and can control where you go, rather then on a pre-determined path.\
