    "11080177870301778702007/11/01 21:18:32ChickenThe task itself is not hard but unfortunately with anything less than a green latency bar you're pretty much screwed. I've wasted so many crystals trying to get past 6 steps simply because all it takes is one lag spike then you end up with 2 colors pinging at the same time... that throws you off then from there it's pretty much over.\
