    "1090120263911938202007/12/17 02:00:24Randsomei just did this and it works great. stealthed passed the initial packs and got in the water.\
\
just aim straight into any of the walls around there, and wall jump. hold the right mouse button, tap space and forward. keep trying, eventually youll stick to the wall. it took me about ten jumps to get to the ledge up top. go back into stealth, and walk to land. the guys in the hallway will turn towards you, but even as a balance druid with no points in any improved stealth they didn't aggro when i walked between them. go turn in your quest and your home free!",
    "109017690410769042007/05/03 02:24:08jackpocalypseI soloed the turn-in as a demonology warlock, with the help of soulstone, invisibility pots and swiftness pots.  I also found someone with a saved Slave Pens instance to invite me to their group, to eliminate the first boss.\
\
I soulstoned myself before going into the instance, and ninjaed past the crab dudes.  Just run on one side when they're on the other.  I drank an invis pot to make it through the hallway.  You can then ninja past the patrol in the open room by going to the right and then to the left.  Hide behind the lightpost at the far left side of the island in the middle of the room until both three-packs are clear, and then run across and behind to the two Defenders.  I set my imp on them and drank a swiftness potion.  This is tricky, but you should be able to get far enough down the hallways to not aggro when you pop your SS.\
\
Wait til your SS is back up and SS yourself again.  Use the next invis pot to run up the first ramp.  Summon your voidwalker.  Then wait until your swiftness pot cooldown is up.  When the three pack patrol walks by run the opposite way up the next ramp.  When you see the two pack patrol, set your voidwalker on them, and drink a swiftness potion.  When he's about to die, or you're about to run into the next defender pack (whichever comes first), sac your voidwalker for the shield.  This should put you in a position to pop SS out of aggro from the defenders when they pat back to the ramp you were just on.  Wait until your next invis pot is up and pop SS.  Immediately drink your invis pot and run around the next ramp and jump off into the water.  Jump onto the ledge to the left and ninja past the next three-pack, and the NPC is right there.\
\
I also had the 12 spell dmg + minor run speed meta gem while doing this, that may have helped a bit.\
\
Enjoy wiping in SSC! :D",
