    "1091662077100620772007/04/04 15:18:37darkangelstrikeThe phrase \"Klaatu barada nikto\" originates from the 1951 Cold-War-era science fiction film The Day the Earth Stood Still. The phrase \"Gort! Klaatu barada nikto!\" was used to stop Gort, the robot in the film, from destroying the world.\
