    "9730181789101817892007/11/10 03:15:51SouloniLevel 63 Paladin (Protection) 1H/Shield (6131 HP/8572 Armor)\
\
Soloed this quest with moderate difficulty. My gear was pretty decent at the time, with mostly Str/Stamina/S.Dmg variant gear from instances/quests --  and the rest Warrior type gear. I was fully enchanted with stamina save for head and shoulder pieces.\
\
The fight started off really great -- Basically a mainstay of Crusader Judgement and Seal of Righteousness. I would keep Holy Shield up 100% of the time, and HoJ when my HP reached about half. During the HoJ is a great time to activate the Ancient Crystal Talisman trinket and refresh Righteousness. This is when I started using Consecrate -- and subsequently he started blasting me into the distance. 1 Bubble, a Bandage, Arcane Torrent (for mana), and a Regal Protectorate activation later -- I was able to take him down -- 3 seconds before I would have hit Lay on Hands =D\
\
Lucky break, but with LoH this fight is a breeze for PLDs.",
