    "11070208782102087822007/12/28 13:59:34hellfishMost of the time, the biggest problem for me was keeping in touch with him, not actually dodging the missiles, because he seems slightly faster than you.\
\
What helps most here is learning his path by heart and actually flying in [b]front[/b] of him. This way the missiles won't hit you, because they're fired in the other direction. Just be aware of those moments where he makes this lovely little stunts, because then the missiles will be fired to the front. You propably won't be able to be in front of him all the time, but make sure you take every possible shortcut available. \
\
Just try to be between him and the point he's going to fly next, and you should be fine.",
