    "110709624921894392007/06/03 00:02:25kraniquaTry to stay on top of him. Just watch where he's going though. Also remember to target him before you start because you might lose him through the crystals. Dodge the lightning bolts.",
    "11070165731301657312007/10/10 21:23:38KeanexThis guy was very tricky, took me 11 tries. Personally I found marking him with an icon (While in a party) helped immensely as he will seem to disappear at times. Good luck.",
    "11070193836101938362007/11/30 08:47:24timskiWinning strategy, after a lot of frustration:\
\
- Fly high. His lightning bombs have a finite range - flying above will avoid 99% of the grief.\
