  ["Getting the Bladespire Tanked66"] = {
    "105126665npcBorgrim Stouthammer21151npcBorgrim Stouthammer2115111300",
    "1051223834240238342007/01/24 15:59:37PhaleuxThe part that isn't obvious about this quest is that the ogres have to walk towards the beer for it to count.  I (a priest) was doing this with my rogue friend and at first we were sapping and dropping it at their feet -- this didn't work.  We found a couple of ways of getting it to work\
\
1.  Place one in front of a patrolling Brute and wait for him to walk up to it.  This is how most people will need to do this quest.\
2.  Sap and drop one a few yards away.  Wait for sap to break, or sap something else and he'll notice it and get drunk.\
3.  This was the best way:  Mind soothe!  Use this oft-forgotten priest skill and walk up close, drop the mug and run away.\
\
We found the Brutes and Cooks were the best to try to get drunk for this quest.  Brutes seemed to be the only kind that were patrolling.",
