  ["More Warbeads68"] = {
    "1047768npcWarden Moi'bff Jill18408npcWarden Moi'bff Jill18408Kurenai500",
    "104771510430151042006/12/13 17:56:48HazellunaWarbead are more easily farmed in the two caves on either side of the Halanni Basin in Nagrand.  If you have a flying mount there are additional higher level mobs in the hills in middle western Nagrand.",
    "1047733301130333012007/02/09 19:28:15GawynAssuming you start at 0/12000 honored, to grind ogres to exalted would take roughly 1238 kills.\
\
MATH:\
Honored rep (12k) + Revered rep (21k) = 33k Rep Points\
Drop Rate on Ogres (33%), 10 rep per ogre, 500 rep per Turn-in.\
So, about 30 kills per turn-in, that's 300 rep (kills) + 500 rep (turn-in) = 800 rep for 30 kills, so...\
\
33,000 divided by 800 rep = 41.25\
41.25 x 30 kills = 1237.5 or 1238 Ogre Kills.\
\
:)",
    "1047729576101277172007/02/02 17:25:50kandarzYou can turn these in all the way to exalted.",
