    "10353105237201052372007/06/16 02:39:07DarthshatnerA word to the wise: stay well away from the dead bodies strewn about the cave. That twitching isn't a graphical glitch; they're infected with parasites, and if you walk over the body, a parasite will spawn and aggro you. Pretty annoying.",
