    "103533193570319352007/02/06 22:10:15FlyvWhen you start this quest, you get a \"Reflection of Ya-six\" as a guardian and a 10 minute debuff before you can summon it again. You then have to walk south and around to go up a level in the cave before getting to Arconus. He'll fight with you if you're attacked, but is quite squishy.",
