    "10353160457501604572007/09/29 17:28:42NeonGenesisIf you're doing this quest, you are probably also doing the quest [URL=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10345]The Flesh Lies...[/URL]. If not, you should pick it up. It's just outside, a little bit west of the entrance of the cave.\
