[b]/use Skyguard Blasting Charges[/b]\
at the end.",
    "11055201378402013782007/12/14 20:56:15yerminsvThis [b]daily quest[/b] is the easiest quest for Netherwing.\
This lazy peons are everywhere at [b]Netherwing Ledge[/b] (Netherwing Ledge is an island at [b]70,85[/b] in [b]Shadowmoon Valley[/b]). Don't forget u must be at least [b]Friendly[/b] with [b]Netherwing[/b] to get this quest.\
\
