\
Disobedient Dragonmaw Peon can be:\
[ul]\
[li] sleeping peons;[/li]\
[li] peons with \"daized\" stars around head;[/li]\
[li] angry red argessive peons.[/li]\
[/ul]\
\
For quest going easier and more comfortable create and use next [b]macro[/b]:\
\
[i]/target Disobedient Dragonmaw Peon\
/use Booterang\
/cleartarget[/i]\
\
Good luck!\
\
[small]-----\
Gugenoth, Stonemaul[/small]",
