    "10929207323102073232007/12/26 00:51:28HuskyTheHuskyI have absolutely no idea why this quest says 'group'. I did it near the guards like the post here said and they pretty much owned the sifters and the gnomes. Neither NPC gives exp so dont have to worry about that. \
