    "10308183021401830212007/11/12 16:40:13InfernoManIt all depends on what you are going for.  If you just want strictly Consortium rep, then grind the Heap in netherstorm for these insignias, they also drop a fair amount of netherweave for bandages/tailoring along with some pretty good amounts of silver.  If you want Consortium rep, Kurenai rep, plus netherweave for bandages/tailoring, as well as crystal powder to turn-ins for the research tokens (say going for the riding war talbuk: http://www.wowhead.com/?item=29228) then farm the ogres in Nagrand.  True the drop rate on the beads isn't the best, but as said previously, they are lower level, easier to kill, and you gain three things at once.  Hope this",
    "10308194560211035982007/12/01 18:37:27hannigaholicAlso (correct me if I'm wrong) but with the Nagrand warbeads I think you have to choose which faction to hand them in to, so you don't get Kurenai rep from handing them into the Consortium NPC.\
