    "10308199899301998992007/12/11 21:43:13xxxthanosxxxI tried grinding for beads on the ogres last nite and ended up with 180+ netherweave, 83 Runecloth, 3 greens and 80 beads in 65 minutes. Thats 2000 rep.\
