\
So to me in only one trial at each, the Zaxxis drop rate and possibility of keys made it a much better choice for straight rep, but the ogres definately balanced out the time with the additional amount of cloths. Plus I had no competition for the ogres, I still ran Zaxxis without having to search for mobs but there were 2 other people farming there.",
    "10308181563101815632007/11/09 14:19:08jrinckMy drop rate for the insignias has consistently sucked over the past two months.  I farm for these at The Heap, and I'm lucky to get better than a 33% drop rate.  Typical is 20%.  I get a much better drop rate on the warbeads in Nagrand.",
