    "10293131585101315852007/08/03 09:25:36blupacheThere is an area around 48,17 where you're at the bottom of a hill with a large crystal outcrop on the other side. I found him patrolling past there & pulled him in. Using the crystal/hill as a brace I was uninterrupted for the 6 or 7 minutes it took me to kill him (resto shammies: we've never killed anything quickly ;) ).\
