    "1064238581780385812007/02/19 07:50:41SihmmThis is the start of the [b]Teron Gorefiend[/b] quest chain, for the [b]Alliance[/b].\
\
This chain begins differently depending on whether you're Alliance (A) or Horde (H):\
\
[b]Alliance[/b] - starts in Wildhammer Stronghold from [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=21774]Zorus the Judicator[/url]:\
1. (A) [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10642][69] A Ghost in the Machine[/url]\
2. (A) [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10643][69] Harbingers of Shadowmoon[/url]\
3. (A) [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10644][70] Teron Gorefiend - Lore and Legend[/url]\
\
[b]Horde[/b] - starts in Shadowmoon Village from [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=21772]Chief Apothecary Hildagard[/url]:\
1. (H) [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10624][69] A Haunted History[/url]\
2. (H) [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10625][69] Spectrecles[/url]\
3. (H) [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10633][70] Teron Gorefiend - Lore and Legend[/url]\
\
At this point the chain splits into three parts which can be done in any order (and by both factions):\
4a. [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10635][70] Divination: Gorefiend's Cloak[/url]\
4b. [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10636][70] Divination: Gorefiend's Truncheon [2 players][/url]\
4c. [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10634][70] Divination: Gorefiend's Armor [5 players][/url]\
\
After collected Gorefiend's stuff and returned it to the [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=21797]spirit[/url], you will get:\
5. (A) [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10645][70] Teron Gorefiend, I am...[/url]\
5. (H) [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10639][70] Teron Gorefiend, I am...[/url]\
\
For this final quest, Gorefiend becomes your \"pet\" and you control him using a pet bar.  Having used him to kill Karsius, you return to Zorus or Hildagard to claim your reward.  Choose from:\
[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=31104]Evoker's Helmet of Second Sight[/url] (cloth DPS headpiece)\
[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=31109]Stealther's Helmet of Second Sight[/url] (leather melee headpiece)\
[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=31110]Druidic Helmet of Second Sight[/url] (leather magical headpiece)\
[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=31106]Stalker's Helmet of Second Sight[/url] (mail +AP headpiece)\
[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=31107]Shamanistic Helmet of Second Sight[/url] (mail +dmg headpiece)\
[url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=31105]Overlord's Helmet of Second Sight[/url] (plate DPS headpiece)\
\
Edit: converted to new [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?help=comment-formatting]tag format[/url] to fix URL overload problem.",
