    "10675100468701004682007/06/08 00:42:01DartteonTheres actually a tube behind the \"circle\" to gauge how many more you need to kill before  he is summoned. The tube will \"suck\" the souls of the dead energy-men, and what looks like electricity will fill the tube from bottom to the brim, then the prince will be summoned.",
    "10675152628901526282007/09/13 19:35:55RituidoJust to elaborate a bit more on the summoning process here... The tube near the transporter in the middle of this area needs to fill up with (5-6, can't remember) yellow balls, which appear when you kill any of the Ethereals in the area.You need to kill two Ethereals to get one of the yellow balls to pop up. The large yellow blobs that hover from the corpse of the Ethereal toward the tube have some travel time. so don't get frustrated if the tube isn't filling up at a rate you're happy with.\
