    "106843784520378452007/02/17 23:46:36licheeVery easy as was mentioned before. It's a single kill. Fly to the back of the building and drop down onto the balcony to fight him. Be wary, he's a healer so if you're a feral, save points up to Maim him and interrupt his heal.",
    "106849262821461582007/05/28 17:28:53ClobberGirlI did this at level 69, human holy/discipline priest, hence no flying mount. \
\
Basically, there's a path into the ruins on the northern side, right next to the building where Oronu is. Enter there and begin clearing your way to the building. Watch out for pats, there are a lot of them. I had to kill 10-15 mobs to get to him. \
\
As for fighting Oronu, if you're a priest without silence, mana burn is your friend. All he did when I fought him was melee me and try to heal himself, and without his mana for healing he's nothing. Just make sure he doesn't have a grounding totem up when you try to mana burn him.",
