    "1029917149011248442007/10/19 00:58:59AmanitaDefinitely stick around near the console. I never noticed anything happening, and kept clicking on it. Then I noticed messages in chat giving me a two minute countdown, then one minute, then 30 seconds, 10 seconds, then done. Pretty easy quest, nice gold. :) Bonus!",
