    "103293717170371712007/02/16 18:20:49DeclannicPretty easy... just make sure you clear the room of everyone first, you don't have to worry about the wings just the main room.  Then click on the control console and wait.  You have 2 minutes to wait.  After about 1 minute some low health technicians start coming in trying to abort it.  Drop them as they never came more than one at a time for me.\
