    "103298982420898242007/05/24 19:22:17ChetarrEverything is correct as far as killing everything in the room and the low lvl techs....but I found him in the hallway @ 24.70 inside the building.",
    "103294681950468192007/03/05 23:29:04AmbushedWhen the mobs spawn to try and shut down, you can sap them. Any sapped mobs will despawn when shutdown is complete",
