    "102187728551735992007/05/03 18:55:40FarmbuyerThis is incorrect.  I have finished the quest on multiple characters, and on every occasion, there was at least one other person also with the quest, and who received credit for it.  Once, the entire group had the quest, and we all received credit for it.\
\
