    "102182815711281312007/01/31 08:28:36MattHockJust an FYI, the adds don't have to spawn. Get CC going on the casters, and quickly kill the ones that aren't CC'd. The elemental adds spawn after a certain time that the casters spend out of CC.\
\
That said, it's still a horribly difficult quest if you aren't massively outgearing/outlevelling it.",
    "10218152471101524712007/09/13 12:21:06DoyceSo let me ask this burning question:\
\
