    "1021812323741735992007/07/19 08:40:06GruneunLast night, we had all four players in our group successfully complete the quest in one run.  Unlike the standard escort quests, there is an object (the floating cube) that each player must use before any player speaks to the NPC.  This cube completes the prerequisite quest.  Just make sure that nobody talks to the NPC until everyone completes the cube portion and everything will be fine.",
    "10218153320111524712007/09/15 12:11:01AtrairaYes, he will have a yellow ! over his head.",
