    "10218199972101999722007/12/12 02:05:02KillahbabeThis escort is bugged sometimes I think.  Our complete group had the quest in their log, including me, and it showed the complete group was sharing it.  For some reason though, me and another guy in the group did not receive any update or reward after completing, even though we did it flawlessly and always were within close range with the escorted guy.  So I guess I'll have to do this again...",
