    "10973157325101573252007/09/23 19:05:25swotamIf you are working on Consortium rep this quest isn't the best use of your keys. This quest and the follow-on grant 1000 rep total. Using the 5 keys and turning in 5 Prisoner ID Catalogue's will get you 1250 rep so all things being equal you are better to skip this and keep turning them in for 250 rep each. Of course, once you hit exalted with them then it's a different story :-)",
