    "109739225520922552007/05/28 06:27:30DiasisShould also note, that you gain 500 rep with Consortium when you turn in the 5 keys.",
    "1097388521300885212007/05/23 14:07:04casualblairSo you got this far and you're probably wondering \"what next?\"\
\
When I got here, the quests weren't filled in, so here is what happens:\
\
1) You've already done the prequests and started on your keys.  Key drop is low as stated above.  5% sounds right.\
\
2) All ethereals drop them, but the ones around mana forge ultris seem to have the best drop rate.\
\
3) They are SELLABLE.  Do not make these cheap as they are a pain in the ass, as below...\
\
4) You hand in your first key and get your follow up.  5 Keys.\
\
5) Hand in 5 keys, and go to Bashir's Landing in BEM (North)\
\
6) Open Stasis Chamber Alpha and fight an 80,000 hp Gronn.  Does a knockback attack (probably aggro wiping, but i dont know...) and a daze attack, but hey Blizzard:  If you're going to make a quest say \"5 man\" dont make the mob fearable.  Solo'd the mob with a mage friend taking out repops.  8 minute fight :P\
\
