           Enjoy :P\
\
8) Hand in mark for key to open stasis chamber in heroic mana tombs.  I think this will iether be a new room with new boss and a whole lot of treasure.  Enjoy phat loots.",
    "10973144170101441702007/08/26 04:14:46HeimdallenOK, here's my question. I know the pre-req is the Ethereum Secrets, which turns into Ethereum Prisoner ID Catalogue...but that quest is repeatable for rep. I've done it a few times, and this quest (A Thousand Words) is not available yet. At what point does it decide you've done a repeatable rep quest enough to let you turn 5 keys into a stasis chamber key? (I'm exalted with consortium).",
