    "108849606430960642007/06/02 17:02:56AjaksRan the instance with Feral Druid, Fire Mage, Affliction Lock, Holy Paladin, Holy Paladin. Took us at least 90 minutes to clear the whole thing. I can confirm that you can get the quest item after 2 npc's have been executed. After he killed one we got a 10 minute debuff. After he killed the second one we got a 15 minute debuff. Tips for clearing are watch out for assassin after the first boss while clearing through the hallway full of archers and spawns. The 2nd boss with 2 archers is simple to kill and his adds are pretty weak if you want to kill them first. Don't rush yourselves into a wipe, because theres a enough time for a slow steady clear.",
